# Multi-agent personas (Cross Section Studio)

Use for **product-sized** work (features, refactors, UX flows). For needle bugfixes, use the short path in `AGENTS.md`: Scout → Implementer → Verifier.

Map each persona to a Cursor `subagent_type`. Do **not** invent stack choices that fight this repo (Streamlit + `pipeline.build_cross_section()` only).

## Role → Cursor mapping

| Persona | `subagent_type` | Mode | Writes? |
|---------|-----------------|------|---------|
| **Product Manager (PM)** | `explore` then optional `generalPurpose` | Spec only | Markdown under `docs/` or `orchestration_reports/` only |
| **Software Architect** | `explore` (readonly) | Design only | Mermaid + module plan in chat / `docs/`; no engine code |
| **Lead Developer** | `generalPurpose` | One module boundary | Code in that boundary only |
| **QA / Code Reviewer** | `bugbot` and/or `security-review` | Read-only | Findings only; reject → Developer |
| **DevOps / Test Runner** | `shell` | Tests only | No source edits; run E2E gate |

## Personas (detail in prompt stubs)

1. **PM** — scope, stories, non-goals → `scripts/agent_prompts/pm.md`; hard rules in `AGENTS.md`.
2. **Architect** — module touch-list, contracts, Mermaid → `scripts/agent_prompts/architect.md`; boundaries in `borehole-platform-architecture.mdc`.
3. **Lead Developer** — one boundary per pass, `build_cross_section()` validation → `scripts/agent_prompts/implement.md`.
4. **QA Reviewer** — diff review, module-boundary + geology integrity → `scripts/agent_prompts/review.md` (+ `security.md` when auth/secrets touched).
5. **DevOps Verifier** — E2E gate, no source edits → `scripts/agent_prompts/verify.md`; `VERIFY_COMMANDS` in `AGENTS.md`.

## Recommended feature pipeline

`User idea → PM → Architect → Lead Developer × N (by boundary) → QA Reviewer → DevOps Verifier → Done` (or CI triage). Skip PM + Architect for single-file fixes.

## Prompt stubs

| Persona | Prompt template | Runtime |
|---------|-----------------|---------|
| Scout | `scripts/agent_prompts/scout.md` | SDK + IDE |
| PM | `scripts/agent_prompts/pm.md` | IDE only |
| Architect | `scripts/agent_prompts/architect.md` | IDE only (`{pm_spec}` optional) |
| Developer | `scripts/agent_prompts/implement.md` | SDK + IDE |
| QA | `scripts/agent_prompts/review.md` | SDK + IDE |
| Security review | `scripts/agent_prompts/security.md` | IDE (`security-review` subagent) |
| CI triage | `scripts/agent_prompts/ci_triage.md` | IDE (`ci-investigator`) |
